snippet.title: Call of the Sea - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Call of the Sea on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1042490/Call_of_the_Sea/
Find out more about Call of the Sea: https://www.calloftheseagame.com/

Call of the Sea will launch on Dec. 8, 2020, on Xbox Series X, Xbox One and Windows PC via Steam, GOG.com and the Microsoft Store. It will also be available with Xbox Game Pass and Xbox Game Pass for PC. 

Call of the Sea is an otherworldly tale of mystery and love set in the 1930s, South Pacific. Explore a lush island paradise, solve puzzles and unlock secrets in the hunt for your husband’s missing expedition.
